            "cell_text_1_3": "Cell 3",
            "cell_text_1_4": "Cell 4",
            "cell_text_1_5": "Cell 5",
            "cell_text_2_1": "How to fix it?",
            "cell_text_2_2": "Tilt your hand slightly toward the light.Move the camera around and see which angle lights up your diamond best.This especially helps for engagement hand pics where details like bangles or mehendi add beauty.",
