        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How To Take Stunning Engagement Ring Pictures On Your Phone",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How To Take Stunning Engagement Ring Pictures On Your Phone</h2><p>You do not need a professional camera. Your phone is enough if you know what to do.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how-to"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kNMkKK": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Find Your Perfect Light",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Find Your Perfect Light</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_bc3071d3-6f47-4612-982f-1764329bedca.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Good light is the biggest factor in beautiful engagement ring photos.</p><p>Some of the best lighting suggestions are ensuring that your setting has soft natural light pouring in or a cloudy day or you are positioned near a window. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_i3xMr3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Find Your Perfect Light Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>It is important that you avoid direct sunlight or yellow indoor lights because they will create a glare, taking away the beauty of the ring.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dEkM3m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Cute + Easy Hand Poses That Always Look Good",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Cute + Easy Hand Poses That Always Look Good</h3>",
            "custom_id": "pear"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_8912f9a5-5de4-4b6e-92bc-9f662ef18fcb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Here are some natural poses that work for every style of engagement ring poses.<br/>Resting your hand on a soft surface so that your hands look relaxed .<br/>Holding your partners hand is always the perfect pose for sweet engagement ring couple photos.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8iXcb3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Cute + Easy Hand Poses Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Holding a coffee mug or bouquet adds texture and dimension to your ring pic without distracting from the ring.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Add Your Partner for Cute Couple Shots",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Add Your Partner for Cute Couple Shots</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_0f175032-32be-4047-94c3-0033e77bf139.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Your story becomes more meaningful when the photo includes both of you. Try:</p><ul><li>Interlocked fingers</li><li>Your hand on their chest</li><li>Them holding your hand from below</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_KEBWWA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Add Your Partner  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>These are perfect couple ring poses and ring ceremony engagement couple poses that feel natural and genuine.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTfgNx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Capture the Ring in Action",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Capture the Ring in Action</h2><p>Instead of staged shots, try action moments. This makes your engagement ring pics feel authentic. Some shots you can take for these candid-like moments are pouring coffee, holding a flower, flipping through a book, cheering with drinks or even just simply walking with your partner. </p><p>These moments are perfect for engagement ring photo ideas.</p>",
            "custom_id": "capture"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BfYxxj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Props That Actually Look Good, Without Looking Forced",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Props That Actually Look Good, Without Looking Forced</h2><p>Gone are the days when you needed to book a studio for a backdrop that looks forced. If you are looking for some props that look aesthetically pleasing without overpowering the image then some of the most popular prop choices are flowers, soft fabrics, your engagement box</p><p>Books, and coffee cups.  Avoid props that are too bright or busy that would take the attention away from the ring.</p>",
            "custom_id": "props"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jGPUrV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Princess Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Check Your Phone Camera Settings </h2><p>Small tweaks make a huge change in your pictures</p><p>Here are some must follow tips to click a picture of your engagement ring that help your image’s quality not get compromised. Always ensure that you clean your lens. In the camera app, tap to focus on the ring. This small detail can elevate the entire image. Lock exposure and shoot in portrait mode. These settings keep the ring crisp and clear. </p><p>You can also use 2x zoom for sharper shots. Use your phone’s portrait or macro mode for detailed engagement ring pics. Capture the facets, the band design, the side angles and the prongs.  These close ups show craftsmanship beautifully.</p>",
            "custom_id": "princess"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ND9GCy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution</h2><p>Every generation redefines what love and luxury mean. For today’s couples, its no longer just about sparkle, its about significance and that's where lab grown diamonds change the story. They offer the same beauty, brilliance and durability as mined diamonds but with a smaller environmental footprint.</p><p>They make it possible to invest in higher clarity or larger carat, all while choosing sustainably. </p><p>Say yes to diamonds that shine not only brighter, but truer, inside and out.</p>",
            "custom_id": "lab-grown"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WhjVYq": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10_262d448f-da8f-455a-95e4-b0ef5bfcb7fb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A delicate twist on a classic, the split shank design adds depth and balance while keeping the silhouette clean. The side detailing catches light beautifully like a small touch to its character. Its elegant enough for everyday wear yet special enough for a lifetime.</p><p>Say yes if you love intricate designs that symbolise how your meant-to-be story unfolded over time. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_7bhRtt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Geometric, sharp, and endlessly radiant, this princess cut is the modern bride’s statement. It’s edges sparkle with precision, giving it a sleek, architectural appeal.</p><p>It’s perfect for those who love clarity and confidence in design <br/>Say yes if you want a ring that feels powerful yet feminine, a ring that moves with poise in every gesture.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cPbJNJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Custom Designs",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Custom Designs</h2><p>When love doesn't fit a mold, neither should your ring. That's why Lucira’s bespoke design experience begins with your story. Every detail, from the curve of the band to the way light hits your diamond, becomes a reflection of you. Maybe it's a hidden engraving that only you two know about. Maybe it's a diamond color inspired by the first city you travelled to together, a soft curve that mirrors the bridge of Paris or warm gold tone that reminds you of sunsets of Santorini. Or maybe its a design that feels nothing like what you’ve seen before because love in your world looks a little different.</p><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, our artisans turn emotions into form, sketch by sketch, setting by setting. Because the most meaningful rings are not just worn, they’re lived in.</p><p>So if your love deserves something that feels deeply, unmistakably yours, create with us.</p>",
            "custom_id": "custom"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion - The Final Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: Your Yes, Your forever </h2><p>Choosing an engagement ring is both emotional and practical, a mix of instinct and intention. The right one won't just look beautiful; it will feel like home.</p><p>Whether it's the confidence of the radiant solitaire, the modern geometry of the princess cut or the tenderness of the heart shaped ring, each piece in Lucira Jewelry’s collection is designed to capture one thing, that perfect unforgettable yes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
